{"title":"学霸的极限","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3521","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>  LBJ是OIER大学霸，话说他刚进电教时，考试得分为1，第二次考试得分也为1，以后每次考试的分数均为前两次考试的和。于是他的成绩以超人的速度上升。但每次考试的总分是恒定的，因此当他的分数达到了一个极限后就不能再增长。现在LBJ想知道自己在哪次考试会达到极限，并求出极限是多少分。 </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>只有一行，即每次考试的总分，为一个正整数N。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>两行，第一行为达到极限的考试次数，第二行为极限分数。<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; \"></span><br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>12</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>6</p><p>8</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>N in (10，10^9)</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}